i don't know what happend or where the prror is, but the 2nd and 3rd episode's audio quality is very poor, im watching this on a 42" 200hz tv, and 7.1 surround reciever and a 12inch subwoofer, but uses 8ch stereo automaticly unless the digital input detects 5.1 surround or better. but.... still these 2 movies is the only ones i've got among the other 200 movies on my HDD that sounds like i was watching this with some laptop-speakers, or built-in-monitor speakers.... and in episode 3 i hear clicking sounds from time to time, besides some wierd music is pretty loud behind the original sound.

pls man... you are the only one who have uploaded these 3 StarWars episodes in HD, would really like if you could fix the sound tho.

besides this torrent, i love KD-releases
